  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个时序图，展示第一帧的渲染流程。核心场景是：Application 发起更新，Tileset 负责选择瓦片，然后异步获取资源，但最后没有瓦片需要立即渲染。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application",
        "Tileset",
        "Frame 1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以 Application 和 Tileset 都是参与者，但 Application 是主动触发方对吧？另外，异步获取资源需要引入额外的角色吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application",
        "Tileset"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Application 作为 actor。异步获取需要 IAssetAccessor，还有一个 IPrepareRendererResources 虽然这帧没直接交互，但作为资源准备接口应该画出来。另外要在顶部加个注释框标明这是 Frame 1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application",
        "IAssetAccessor",
        "IPrepareRendererResources",
        "Frame 1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我已经把四个角色排好了：Application、Tileset、IAssetAccessor、IPrepareRendererResources，顶部加了 Note 标注 Frame 1。现在画第一条消息：Application 指向 Tileset 的 updateView。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application",
        "Tileset",
        "updateView",
        "Frame 1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来 Tileset 内部要做选择，标成自调用消息：Select Tiles A, B。然后启动两个异步获取，分别用虚线箭头指向 IAssetAccessor，标注 Start: get (Tile A) 和 Start: get (Tile B)。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Tileset",
        "IAssetAccessor",
        "Tile A",
        "Tile B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "异步消息用开箭头对吧？我已经画好了两条异步获取。但最后返回给 Application 的消息有点奇怪——你说这帧没有瓦片要渲染？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Tileset",
        "IAssetAccessor",
        "Application",
        "Tile A",
        "Tile B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这是关键设计点。虽然发起了 Tile A 和 Tile B 的异步获取，但它们还没准备好，所以这帧返回的是空。用虚线箭头回 Application，标注 Tiles to Render This Frame (None)。",
